f directors said mr w john short ceo of nutracea he has been a strong supporter of nutracea for several years his knowledge of the dietary role of vegetable proteins in general and our stabilized rice bran products specifically will be invaluable to nutracea as we continue to increase sales in all major global markets henk will participate with other board members in setting strategy for our business and will assist senior management in the execution of our growth plans his relationships with a large number of major global brands will assist us in the development of ingredient inclusion of our stabilized rice bran defatted rice bran rice bran oil and derivative products in a broad range of consumer products nutracea has proprietary and patented intellectual property that allows us to convert rice bran one of the worlds most underutilized food sources into a number of highly nutritious human food and animal nutrition products last year nutracea and beneoremy a world leader in functional food ingredients derived from rice announced an exclusive cobranded sales and marketing agreement under the terms of the distribution and cooperation agreement entered into on september  0 nutracea will produce stabilized rice bran srb for exclusive distribution by beneoremy under their remylive brand in over 0 countries in europe the middle east and africa emea as well as russia india australia and new zealand related articles from twofi view from the top malcolm sheil taste and nutrition division president and ceo europe kerry  jun   kerry group’s new taste and nutrition division president and ceo of europe malcolm sheil has just been permanently appointed to the role following a period serving as interim president from twofi how to back up clean label claims  jun   a “no artificial ingredients” angle is an achievable goal for food manufacturers who wish to protect their brand name and bottom line by backing up their claims with thirdparty testing from twofi dsm expands capabilities